summary: Notification of Establishment of Military Cover Backstop for (INCE: TORING), File No. 5190, 10 Card No. B165617, effective 7 August 1962. Establishes military cover backstop at U.S. Army Element, Joint Operations Group (8739)32. Includes instructions for blocking records, submitting forms for changes or transfers, and ensuring Army W-2 issuance.
title: NOTIFICATION OF ESTABLISHMENT OF MILITARY COVER BACKSTOP
